{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Legislate for a council tax discount for all pensioners",
        "additional_details": "When many pensioners have worked for 50 odd years, paid into a pension, bought their own house, then retire on a lower income, I do not think they should have to pay such a significant amount of council tax.",
        "background": "I feel that current council tax rates do not take pension incomes into account. This means some pensioners are having to pay what I think is a very significant percentage of their pension towards council tax.",
